# Live JSONLs are NOT gitignored anymore. They're piped through
# scripts/sanitize_jsonl.py at sync time which strips account_id, client_id,
# host/port, bot_pid, equity/drawdown, and position detail. The committed
# files are scrubbed. See scripts/sync_quant_bot.sh + sanitize_jsonl.py.
